result.name: Le Velo - The Baker

reviews.text: Get more options for hot food. However still must say enjoyed the menu choices available
Simple, healthy and good quality food. Sandwiches made from fresh bread. Friendly staff and owner.

With all the good review I was expecting something interesting, maybe I ordered the wrong food (beef burger and fries, the beef was tasteless and spongy and floury.... No taste of meat t all), maybe I went during lunch hour (waited 20 min to have my order available for pick up as I was ordering take away, and meanwhile all the ppl ordering after me were gone already with the order) - anyway overall quite a disappointing experience.
Simple good & quality food. Vs Pret, this has local charm.
Excellent service and excellent french food and french bread.  The owner is very nice and cool.
